 *     or object that has a handleEvent method.
 * @param {number=} opt_delay Milliseconds to wait; default is 0.
 * @param {SCOPE=} opt_handler Object in whose scope to call the listener.
 * @return {number} A handle to the timer ID.
 * @template SCOPE
